.DT
remove_group
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
remove_group

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remove_group -  This function removes a group from the handler and is only used internally.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int remove_group(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - name of the group to be disbanded
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 if group doesn't exist
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function removes a group from the handler and is only used
internally.  No notification of this is given to players, and
no cleanup is done on their part.
If you want to force the deletion of a group, use disband_group()
instead.

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
disband_group()

.EP

